---
alwaysApply: false
description: .NET filetree specification for gRPC and HTTP services.
---

## Filetree Specification - gRPC service

[Service Name]/
│
├── src/
│ ├── Controllers/V1/ # gRPC API
│ │ └── [gRPC Api service]
│ │
│ ├── Operations/ # Shared business logic
│ │ └── [Domain Operations] # Domain-specific operations
│ │
│ ├── Startup.cs # DI Registration
│ │
│ ├── Settings.cs # Strongly typed project settings with runtime support
│ │
│ └── [Project].csproj # Project file with gRPC dependencies
│
└── authorizations.yml # Api authorization configuration

## Filetree Specification - HTTP service

[Service Name]/
│
├── src/
│ ├── Controllers/ # HTTP REST controllers
│ │ └── [Domain Controllers]  
│ │
│ ├── Models/
│ │ ├── Requests/ # HTTP request DTOs
│ │ └── Responses/ # HTTP response DTOs
│ │
│ ├── Operations/ # Business logic layer
│ │ └── [Domain Operations]  
│ │
│ ├── Startup.cs # DI Registration
│ │
│ ├── Settings.cs # Strongly typed project settings with runtime support
│ │
│ └── [Project].csproj # Project file with dependencies
│
└── authorizations.yml # Api authorization configuration
